import React from 'react';
import { ChakraProvider, Box, Grid, GridItem, Heading, Text, Input, Button, Container, Flex } from '@chakra-ui/react';

const AdminLoginPage = () => {
  return (
    <ChakraProvider>
      <Box>
        {/* Header */}
        <Box bg="teal" p={4} color="white">
          <Container maxW="container.lg">
            <Heading size="lg">Admin Login</Heading>
          </Container>
        </Box>
        
        {/* Main Content */}
        <Grid templateColumns="repeat(5, 1fr)" gap={4} p={4}>
          {/* Left Menu */}
          <GridItem colSpan={1} bg="gray.200" p={4}>
            <Heading size="md">Left Menu</Heading>
            <Box mt={100}>
              <Text>Dashboard</Text>
              <Text>Seller Tool</Text>
              <Text>BuyLeads</Text>
              <Text>Settings</Text>
            </Box>
          </GridItem>

          {/* Login Form */}
          <GridItem colSpan={4}>
            <Box p={4}>
              <Heading size="md" mb={4}>Login</Heading>
              <Input placeholder="Username" mb={4} />
              <Input type="password" placeholder="Password" mb={4} />
              <Button colorScheme="teal">Login</Button>
            </Box>
          </GridItem>
        </Grid>

        {/* Footer */}
        <Box bg="teal" p={4} color="white" mt={4}>
          <Container maxW="container.lg">
            <Flex justifyContent="center">
              <Text>Footer Content</Text>
            </Flex>
          </Container>
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </ChakraProvider>
  );
};

export default AdminLoginPage;
